children.text: The holes in the HyJoist floor joists have been located too close to the support.
‘Holes may be cut through the web of HyJoist provided they are located within the central part of the span as specified below’ ;

As the present locations of these holes breaches the manufacturer’s requirements, the builder should confirm the acceptability with the manufacturer and either rectify these joists as directed, or supply the owner with certification from the manufacturer that the as-built is acceptable.
